      <caption>Car loan interest costs — ₹8 lakh loan at various rates, 5-year tenure</caption>
      <thead><tr><th>Interest Rate</th><th>Monthly EMI</th><th>Total Interest Paid</th><th>Total Outflow</th></tr></thead>
